<item>
            <title>[OAK-7252] Function index for name() and localname() don&apos;t allow sorting</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-7252</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is no way currently to have indexed based sorting on nodename - function index implementation for node name and local name doesn&apos;t provide correct order entry that would match a property definition for corresponding function index.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13137047">OAK-7252</key>
            <summary>Function index for name() and localname() don&apos;t allow sorting</summary>
