                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="16356454" author="catholicon" created="Thu, 8 Feb 2018 03:55:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=thomasm&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;thomasm&quot;&gt;thomasm&lt;/a&gt;, afaics, &lt;tt&gt;NodeNameImpl&lt;/tt&gt; should have following to allow sorting on node name:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;diff --git a/oak-core/src/main/java/org/apache/jackrabbit/oak/query/ast/NodeNameImpl.java b/oak-core/src/main/java/org/apache/jackrabbit/oak/query/ast/NodeNameImpl.java
index cd1a884d9e..b5bce13e11 100644
--- a/oak-core/src/main/java/org/apache/jackrabbit/oak/query/ast/NodeNameImpl.java
+++ b/oak-core/src/main/java/org/apache/jackrabbit/oak/query/ast/NodeNameImpl.java
@@ -186,7 +186,7 @@ public class NodeNameImpl extends DynamicOperandImpl {
             return null;
         }
         return new OrderEntry(
-                QueryConstants.RESTRICTION_NAME, 
+                QueryConstants.FUNCTION_RESTRICTION_PREFIX + getFunction(s),
             Type.STRING, 
             o.isDescending() ? 
             OrderEntry.Order.DESCENDING : OrderEntry.Order.ASCENDING);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(similar change is required for local name too... I just am not sure if I&apos;m thinking in the right direction)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16358073" author="tmueller" created="Fri, 9 Feb 2018 08:27:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think it makes sense to deprecate &quot;indexNodeName&quot; and &quot;:nodeName&quot; in the Lucene index, and always use function indexes. That way, we can enable sorting, spellcheck, even on uppercase / lowercase variants.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16358995" author="catholicon" created="Fri, 9 Feb 2018 21:32:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed on trunk at &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1823707&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;r1823707&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16454143" author="edivad" created="Thu, 26 Apr 2018 13:22:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Bulk close 1.9.0&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
